desc: Liz Franklin is a celebrity esthetician and owner of Skin Society located in Granite Bay, Ca. Liz offers a variety of spa services including facials, bio-dermabrasion, CBD treatments, and waxing. Each service comes with a custom selection of products suitable for your skin, all which are available for order online.

layout.text: By using effective and natural products, I can help you achieve optimal skin health with amazing results.
